fulltitle: Douglas Valentine: CIA, Drug Trafficking, and the JFK Assassination (2011)
title: Douglas Valentine: CIA, Drug Trafficking, and the JFK Assassination (2011)

description:
VISIT: https://archive.politicalassassinations.net/
This is a talk from the 2011 Coalition on Political Assassinations Conference. Douglas Valentine, author of Strength of the Pack discusses the nexus of CIA drug trafficking and the JFK Assassination. Original video of the talk came from on COPA's ustream channel (no longer available).

For more related content, please visit: 
http://ourhiddenhistory.org/
https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
